&lt;li&gt;We want builders. No hand-holding. No fluff. No fake projects. No slide decks. No sitting in meetings all day. Just raw engineering, real hardware, and real flight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You must thrive under pressure, learn fast, troubleshoot in the field, and push hardware to its limits. We move fast. We go to&amp;nbsp;&lt;strong&gt;Mojave at 4 am in the morning&lt;/strong&gt;. We expect results and an obsession with quality and speed&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;You will be a core executor of flight systems, taking them from concept to reality and driving rapid iteration loops. You will work across design, integration, testing, and flight. If you want real ownership, real hardware, and real flight milestones, this is it.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p&gt;No tourists. No bystanders. Only builders.&lt;/p&gt;
