&lt;li&gt;Own mechanical subsystems from concept to flight&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Perform first-principles sizing, trade studies, and rapid iteration&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build, test, break, and refine flight hardware&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support integration, production, and flight operations&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Work closely with avionics, GNC, power, RF, and software teams&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
