&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Analyze and verify test site conditions to ensure successful conduct of a flight test; sound judgement in aviation safety, preflight analysis of atmospheric conditions, and adherence to regulations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Assemble, configure, and prepare aircraft for flight, including mechanical, electrical, and payload setup.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run preflight inspections and checklists, and make the call on whether the aircraft is ready.&lt;/li&gt;
