&lt;li&gt;Act as the calm, decisive voice on the sticks when something goes wrong in the air.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Run launch and recovery, including any non-traditional takeoff and landing configurations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
