&lt;li&gt;Analyze flight logs and telemetry, run root cause analysis, and write up quick-look and formal test reports.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Build tooling and scripts that speed up setup, data review, and field operations.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Own the technical interface between flight operations and the engineering team.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
