&lt;li&gt;Define what we measure: instrumentation, sensors, data acquisition, and telemetry requirements.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Write test plans and hazard analyses, and contribute to flight safety documentation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Translate engineering questions into test points that can effectively find an answer.&lt;/li&gt;
