&lt;li&gt;Recommend and make parameter changes when the test calls for it, in coordination with the test director and flight crew.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Capture the conditions, configuration, and events of every flight with precision.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
